room_title: Escape room "Alphabet Soup" by Escape Room at the Nest in Canton
review: Just did the alphabet soup room. It was lots of fun. We had six in the room and it was a great number. The two guys that run the room are very nice, too. I would definitely recommend this and we will be back to do another room. 5 stars
